And, we have had this class name

00:28:06.096 --> 00:28:06.916 A:middle
field for a while.

00:28:07.286 --> 00:28:08.346 A:middle
And, we want to encourage you to

00:28:08.346 --> 00:28:10.176 A:middle
use that as a display name in

00:28:10.176 --> 00:28:12.036 A:middle
your MDM console, as well as

00:28:12.036 --> 00:28:13.526 A:middle
what you pass along to Classroom

00:28:13.526 --> 00:28:15.096 A:middle
